ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"政府 兩字轉 議會 覺得點？"},{"pid":"0f09bc9183c701ea117096df2c72762574990943","tid":1332661,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da8c50c358bf3d8842c14cf86997addec98931f8","tid":1332661,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"政府 兩字轉 議會 覺得點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港政府 照樣唔理 新定既臨時議會 係吹佢唔脹..."},{"pid":"8d9348f856ea8825e4c3dd8a8f11880993d71f97","tid":1332661,"uid":32204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"我記得當時游蕙禎都寫過信畀蔡英文，樓主可以睇返當年回覆，台灣當你派膠<br />\n<br />\n你認真咁搞到時連成個國際社會都畀粒膠我哋<br />\n<br />\n定係樓主覺得今次有乜唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e021563dadbb3ad06909c09438030091007e77f9","tid":1332661,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">一定要人 一定要幫 一定要去 各位努力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Spread it!</div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>1）有人講咗「唔好再覆」就唔好爭住屌一毛、恥笑一毛，亦唔好跟住留「唔好再覆」，否則等同推po。2）俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。3）新聞po睇日期先覆，小心一毛伎倆：有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po。最後，721去遊行！</code><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 七大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"19ea337e27a48cd064e3c996940a507644ecf214","tid":1332661,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8d9348f856ea8825e4c3dd8a8f11880993d71f97","tid":1332661,"uid":32204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"我記得當時游蕙禎都寫過信畀蔡英文，樓主可以睇返當年回覆，台灣當你派膠<br />\n<br />\n你認真咁搞到時連成個國際社會都畀粒膠我哋<br />\n<br />\n定係樓主覺得今次有乜唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"當時香港都未有e家既現況<br />\n又未有國際關注... 點同呢....<br />\n<br />\n我既說法其實係比較能夠比國際有位支持既方法<br />\n<br />\n因為唔借民國為名 基本上好難令國際有能力支持...."},{"pid":"031e3c0d0862cbf8253b812522453ac99982bc8b","tid":1332661,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:17:22.000Z","msg":"冇"}]}